Executive summary
-----------------

This work seeks to harden Apache Cassandra against Byzantine failures.

You can find our client in our forked YCSB project https://github.com/ronili/HardenCassandraYCSB[HardenCassandraYCSB]. 

For more information about Cassandra, see http://cassandra.apache.org/[the Apache Cassandra web site].

